<br>
Like Howling Stones? :-D<br>
As for pre-50, someone posted a nice list earlier. Reading down the list, nearly every one of those places is deserted on my server. What it is, is that EQ players don't want to pull in dungeons. They like wide open areas where they can just run up and smooch the mob and then run back to camp with no problems.<br>
 They like sarnak forts and large deserts. Plus they can get more mobs quicker than if they had to actually plan a pull. What would be cool is if VI lowerd the amount of mobs in Lake of Ill Omen, Oasis, FM and OT. Then some of those players would filter over (back) to High Pass/Keep, Droga/Nurga, etc.<br>
